column5: Yes with me
We talk about why we have poor mental health, possible causes for our poor mental health and how it effects our relationship or just mental health in general really
Omg yes totally get this
Yes I will come and I’ll bring seeds!!
Yes I could bring you lots of mums!
You did tho
I know I want them I have every other flower except these
Yes please thank you
Yes I am is there any thing you were looking for?
I would also let u
Yeah I know sigh Ill figure it out I’m not one to hide who I am so I know It won’t last forever

You changed I didn’t but I can’t blame you. I just want to hold you again and look into your eyes. I want to listen to our songs and go on gas station runs late at night. The pain is unbearable so I just push it away like I did you.
I’m the same way :(
Ok wow this actually sounds good af
Yes but I don’t want to
https://soundcloud.com/goodtry/i-will-never-feel-like-i-did-in-2016
This happened to me last night
Yes it hurts but it’s worth the pain

The music isn’t advocating suicide. Music is just relatable based on you’re mood. She’s obviously not okay so she listens to music that is similar to how she feels. However music can effect your mood so I would advise not listening to sad music if you are already sad and don’t have control over yourself. I can listen to sad music when I’m suicidal and not attempt suicide because I deal with wanting to die everyday but I’m not gonna do it. She’s young tho.
Is it just me or does this look easy to do I feel like it wouldn’t be that hard
Very good would love to hear some lyrics with this
Me too can’t see what made her happy
Yeah definitely not condoning doing this I’m sorry to hear that
Very true but what more can we expect? I know that I ask people this and don’t expect them to tell me the truth and if they did I’m so socially awkward I wouldn’t know how to respond
I’ve started doing the same like “no I’m not thanks for asking” and their “that sucks I’m sorry” is always expected but what else can I expect
Alllll the time or I’ll just sleep so I can live in my dreams
Riiight lmao
Only way I can keep my mind out of the dark place at night
